After a few days down in London I'm back on track and almost finished with the interactive music/video/website to go along with the video for Gideon Conn's song <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eVcgZuF8e20">Crystallised</a>. All the shapes and colours have been generated from Dex Hannon's artwork and the idea is that you'll be able to fly around all the shapes and scenes from the video. I'm building in it <a href="http://www.goocreate.com">GooCreate </a>which is a really powerful engine for WebGL and HTML5 games.
